Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2,"I have had Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 now for a while. And while the game is fairly old, it has aged perfectly.  Modern Warfare in my opinion was one of Call Of Duty's best sidelines. Modern Warfare is right next to the Black Ops sideline, which is another one of my favorites.   Modern Warfare 2 is totally worth the money. I picked MW2 up for about $20 usd. And this game has supplied me with hours of entertainment, without becoming boring.   Now, before you buy the game let me tell you something. I DO NOT ADVISE YOU MAIN THIS GAME. And what I mean by that is that you should not play this game 24/7. The game is almost too old in the Call of Duty line. This game is perfect for when you are bored, and just feel like playing a semi-competitive FPS. That is how I play the game, and that is how I enjoy the game. The reason I am saying not to main this game is because I tried to main the game as soon as I bought it, this lasted about 5 hours. Then I was bored. But hell, who knows, you may play the game for about 2 hours and really like it, and main the game. But from my experience, it just didn't work that way.   But, none the less. This game really provided me with quality entertainment. And has earned a solid 8 on my grading scale.   Graphics - 7 (considering the game is old)  Multiplayer - 8  Story - 6  Missions - 8  Overall - 8"
